            "title": "盤中速報 - 費城半導體大漲2.02%，報8864.87點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間10日09:33，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲175.34點（或2.02%），暫報8864.87點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+10.93%</li><li>近 1 月：+11.26%</li><li>近 3 月：+13.76%</li><li>近 6 月：+27.04%</li><li>今年以來：+22.68%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以邁威爾科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRVL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRVL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRVL-US</a>)領漲。邁威爾科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRVL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRVL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRVL-US</a>)上漲6.52%；安謀控股公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ARM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ARM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ARM-US</a>)上漲4.51%；博通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AVGO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AVGO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AVGO-US</a>)上漲4.27%；和康電訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MTSI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MTSI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MTSI-US</a>)上漲3.46%；超微半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>)上漲2.83%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，美光科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>)下跌0.23%；英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)下跌0.03%。</p></section></main>",
